@startuml DataFlow
title NoSQL Data Flow - Note Creation

actor User
participant "Next.js Frontend" as FE
participant "NestJS Backend" as BE
participant "Mongoose ODM" as ODM
database "MongoDB" as DB

User -> FE: Enters Title, Content, Tags
FE -> FE: Validate Input (Min length)
FE -> BE: POST /api/notes (JSON Payload)

BE -> BE: Global Validation Pipe\n(class-validator)
BE -> ODM: new NoteModel(data).save()

group NoSQL Persistence Logic
    ODM -> DB: BSON Document Insert
    note right of DB: Dynamic Schema:\nNo pre-defined columns\nneeded for Tags array
    DB --> ODM: Success (with _id)
end

ODM --> BE: Document Instance
BE --> FE: 201 Created (JSON Document)
FE -> User: Update UI via TanStack Query
@enduml
